Package ausroulette.model.bet

Class NumberBetImpl

  • java.lang.Object
    • ausroulette.model.bet.NumberBetImpl
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Bet, NumberBet
    public class NumberBetImpl
extends java.lang.Object
implements NumberBet
    A concrete representation of a number bet in the Aussie Roulette game in the Further Programming Assignment.

    This implements the interface NumberBet and is used to represent both BetType.NUMBER and BetType.ZERO bets.

        public int finaliseBet​(Pocket winningPocket)
        Description copied from interface: Bet
        Called when finalising a bet.

        This methods should be used change the state of a bet from being placed (outcome unknown) to being either a win or loss. This state should be able to be retrieved after the bet has been finalised (which would usually occur at the end of a spin).

        Specified by:
        finaliseBet in interface Bet
        Parameters:
